OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA dry and bright start,
OL,6,Fbefore increasing cloud and outbreaks
OL,7,Fof rain, locally heavy, spreads east
OL,8,Facross all parts during the afternoon.
OL,9,FWinds strengthening. Feeling humid.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FVariable
OL,12,Fcloud and brighter spells, with some
OL,13,Fscattered light showers on Friday,
OL,14,Fthese easing later. Breezy. Dry with
OL,15,Fsunny spells on Saturday and Sunday.
OL,16,FFeeling warmer, with lighter winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
